'''Diskspd''' is a [[command-line interface|command-line tool]] for storage [[Benchmark (computing)|benchmarking]] on [[Microsoft Windows]] that generates a variety of requests against [[computer file]]s, [[Disk partitioning|partitions]] or [[Computer data storage|storage devices]] and presents collected statistics as text in the command-line interface or as an [[XML|XML file]].<ref>https://github.com/Microsoft/diskspd/wiki</ref>

